com.iota.iri.utils.collections.impl

Class BoundedSetWrapper<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iota.iri.utils.collections.impl.BoundedSetWrapper<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type parameter
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    BoundedCollection<E>, BoundedSet<E>, java.lang.Iterable<E>, java.util.Collection<E>, java.util.Set<E>

    public class BoundedSetWrapper<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements BoundedSet<E>
    A wrapper for a set that allows up to maxsize elements. Old elements are removed once it is full and new elements are added. The way old elements are chosen depends on the underlying set implementation.
